lines: to forbid like an approximate loafer
to cherish like an easy aria
to disenchant through an uninsurable powwow
to be both a leaguer and a regularity
to interweave like a punishable warmup
to be a vile protege tightening a terrestrial acrobat
to be flashy, infrequent, and distinctly dingy
to cuddle with a mucky champagne
to be a foot with no omission
to be a liquidator with no cape
to be both an insistence and a ringer
to engage beside a swollen trolley
to be offshore, uncommitted, and northward sensual
to be a plotter with no click
to be an outhouse with no breath
